No any programming in .NET, Java, APIs.
There is some scripting using Azure Portal, Powershell Az, Bash/CLI.

JSON for templates and CLI responses.

Azure Cloud Shell -> Bash and Powershell

Microsoft switched from AzureRM module to Az.

Commands Powershell:
1. pwsh -> Command to start powershell on linux
2. Install-Module -Name Az -AllowClobber -Force -> Installs latest Az module
3. Get-InstalledModule -Name Az -AllVersions | Select-Object -Property Name, Version -> Shows versions of installed Az Modules
4. Connect-AzAccount -> To connect to azure account.
5. Get-AzSubscription -> Shows Subscriptions

